text.tspan: Cumulative confirmed COVID-19 deaths vs. cases, Feb 28, 2023
Limited testing and challenges in the attribution of cause of death mean the cases and deaths counts may not be accurate. The gray lines
show the corresponding case-fatality rates (the ratio between confirmed deaths and confirmed cases).
